  "technicalDetails": "<p>Important/Additional Notes: PDF with migration instructions: https://www.dropbox.com/s/4vprqjftfb7hbri/UE5_Instructions.pdf?dl&#61;0</p><p><br /></p><p>Features:</p><p>• 96 impact particles (32 material types with small/medium/large</p><p>variants)</p><p>• 8 fracture particles</p><p>• Impact sound FX for 19 materials and ricochet (also to be expanded</p><p>in later updates).</p><p>• Grenade launcher explosion with shrapnel</p><p>• Frag grenade FX</p><p>• Impact and splatter decals</p><p>• Data table driven FX spawning</p><p>• Example blueprints include ricochet, material modifiers, VFX</p><p>and Sound spawning.</p><p>• Demo map contains a gallery of materials and destructible meshes to</p><p>test the FX.</p><p><br /></p><p>Platforms Tested: Windows</p><p><br /></p><p>Support: info&#64;cubitstudios.com</p><p><br /></p>",
